Package wisedevil.test

This package contains the interfaces, classes and packages for the WiseDevil's Java Test Suit.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTestMethod
    This class represents a generic method of a test case.
    Assert
    This class contains the methods to be used to test the code.
    CleanupMethod
    This class represents a cleanup method for a test case.
    MethodInspector<T>
    This class provides support for fast method inspection.
    PropertyInspector<T>
    This class provides support for fast property inspection.
    SetupMethod
    This class represents a setup method for a test case.
    TestCase
    This class represents a test case.
    TestCaseInfo
    This class contains information about a test case.
    TestCaseInfoBuilder
    Builder class for the TestCaseInfo class.
    TestCaseParser
    This class is a parser for a test case class.
    TestCaseProcess
    Represents a test case process for a class file.
    TestCaseRunner
    This class runs the tests of a given test case class.
    TestMethod
    Represents a test function.
    TestSequence
    Represents a runnable linear sequence of test methods.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TestFailedException
    Thrown to indicate that a test has failed.
    TestProcessAbortedException
    Thrown to indicate that a test has failed.
